{"slug":"evergreen-protocol","name":"Evergreen Protocol","description":"Evergreen Protocol is a modular infrastructure on Solana for tokenizing, trading, and fractionalizing verified forest land as real-world assets. Landowners mint EVG-L tokens backed by geospatial and legal data. A USDC-based vault acquires these tokens and issues EVG-S shares. All assets are tied to environmental commitments and registered via Brazil’s CAR system — creating transparent, legal, on-chain liquidity for conservation.","oneLiner":"Modular Solana infrastructure for tokenizing and fractionalizing verified forest land as real-world assets.","hackathon":{"name":"Breakout","slug":"breakout","startDate":"2025-04-14"},"tracks":[{"name":"DeFi","key":"breakout/defi"},{"name":"Infrastructure","key":"breakout/infrastructure"},{"name":"Stablecoins","key":"breakout/stablecoins"}],"links":{"github":"https://github.com/vivipolli/evergreen-protocol","demo":null,"presentation":"https://www.loom.com/share/dbce48ae1af14eed9ff04ad75cd75bbd?sid=b4b06a4f-6252-4364-b691-e907e5af3dc1","technicalDemo":"https://www.loom.com/share/8a96631a49e74b079546f5ab48a1c884?sid=a8856e90-6006-4ba8-bd07-35e0eb21d904","twitter":"https://twitter.com/nossaterrafirme","colosseum":"https://arena.colosseum.org/projects/explore/evergreen-protocol"},"team":{"count":2,"members":[{"displayName":"vivian polli","username":"vivipolli","githubHandle":null,"twitterHandle":null},{"displayName":"iara vicente","username":"iaravicente","githubHandle":null,"twitterHandle":"iara_vicente"}]},"isWinner":false,"accelerator":null,"createdAt":"2025-05-16T15:48:25.448Z","tags":{"problemTags":["illiquid real estate assets","lack of transparency in conservation","difficulties in forest land monetization","complex legal verification for land"],"solutionTags":["rwa tokenization","fractionalization","geospatial data integration","usdc-backed vaults"],"primitives":["rwa","tokenization","vaults","fractionalization","oracle"],"techStack":["solana","react","v